summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Evanston Avenue from North Forty-first Street to Bowdom Place et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete walks under Ordinance No. 17175, creating Local Improvement District No. 1612 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
